---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import pp from '../../public/placeholder.png'
---

<Layout title="About Kolade Chris">
  <main>
    <div class='bio-text'>
      <h1>About me</h1>
      <p>
        I'm a software developer and technical writer with the hunger to
        provide value anywhere I get to. I work primarily with React, Next JS, JavaScript, CSS, and HTML.
      </p>

      <p>
        I can write an extensive article on any of those technologies and
        make websites with them. Apart from those technologies,
        I can also work with Node JS, Express, Python, Mongo
        DB, and MySQL. Writing is my strength â€” I'm the kind of person that
        can learn new things and write on them right away.
      </p>

      <p>I currently work at freeCodeCamp as an instructional designer. I also work on freelance projects with some incredible people I knew from Twitter. Other times, I work on personal projects I don't ever complete.</p>

      <p>
        You can read my articles on <a class='' href='/services'>freeCodeCamp</a> and <a class='' href='/blog'>my blog</a>. You can learn more about what I do on my <a class='' href='/blog'>service page</a>.
      </p>
      <a class='contact-btn' role="button" href='/contact'>Say Hello</a>
    </div>

    <div class="bio-image">
      <Image
        src={pp}
        src={pp}
        alt="Kolade Chris"
        height={0}
        width={0}
        sizes="100vw"
      />
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>

  main {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10rem;
  }
	h1 {
		font-size: var(--h1-font);
	}

	p {
		font-size: var(--paragraph-font);
	}

  a {
    color: var(--primary-color);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  main div p:nth-child(5) {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .contact-btn {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: unset;
    cursor: pointer;
    background-color: var(--primary-color);
    padding: 0.8rem 1.3rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    font-size: var(--paragraph-font);
    transition: 0.3s ease-in;
  }

  .contact-btn:hover {
    background-color: var(--primary-hover);
  }
</style>